This is a small set of TextMate shortcuts I've begun collecting in one place.

Haml
ul of items from array          lo
ul of linked items from array   llo

Devise/CanCan
before_filters for authentication/authorization   auth

Factory Girl
Factory(:name)                  fg
Factory.build(:name)            fb
Factory.attributes_for(:name)   fa

Jekyll/Textile
Post info yaml      info
Textile link        url
Highlight block     hi

INSTALLATION:

cd ~/"Library/Application Support/TextMate/Bundles/"
git clone git://github.com/ruralocity/Ruralocity.tmbundle.git Ruralocity.tmbundle
osascript -e 'tell app "TextMate" to reload bundles'